# Workflow

## Commands (cwd: `solar-roi-calculator/`)
- Install: `npm install`
- Dev: `npm run dev`
- Build: `npm run build`
- Lint: `npm run lint`
- All tests: `npm run test:run`
- Watch: `npm run test`
- Coverage: `npm run test:coverage`
- Single file: `npm run test:run -- tests/utils/calculations.test.ts`
- Single test: `npx vitest run tests/utils/calculations.test.ts -t "produces a result"`

## Testing
- Run `npm run test:run` after every change. All tests must pass before committing.
- Every new function needs tests: unit (happy path + edge cases), integration for new flows.
- New utility → `tests/utils/`, new model → `tests/models/`, new wizard flow → `tests/integration/`.
- Bug fixes require a regression test that would have caught the bug.

## Commits
One commit per logical chunk with a descriptive message.

## Keeping rules current
Update `.cursor/rules/architecture.mdc` when you: add a shared utility/constant/data pattern, change an architectural contract, add/remove a stub, or change how data files are accessed.
